MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2007-1967. Internatl. Bhd. of Electrical Workers, Local No. 8 v. Court of Common Pleas.

In Procedendo. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of procedendo. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
